  "staticData": null,
  "description": "Smart 6h scheduler: skips when a run is in flight; runs GPU preflight (avail / temp / memory headroom); on pass pulls /api/eval/scores, detects plateau or regression risk, and POSTs an adaptive /api/evolve/start. Slack-notifies start vs skip reasons when SLACK_WEBHOOK_URL is set."
